	   <tr><td colspan=2>If you try to do it with a stein in the bank it will be a huge waste of time.&nbsp;&nbsp;In other words, no you can't get another one until the first is actually out of your possession, neither on your person nor in the bank.<br><br>There are ways around this.  You can create a mule to hold one while you do the second.  Or, you can do the quest all the way up to getting the compendium from Gregor, sell the existing stein, then use the compendium to replace your personal stein.<br><br>It's a good way to fund yourself through those lean years.  As far as other quests, none that I know of until you can do the incandescents and the rod of insidious glamour ones.<br><br>Have fun.<br><br>-Yizz<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
