 ARE all that stands between a bad pull and massive XP regardless what the MA or Cleric think. My job is to keep the whole party alive when they would have NO chance without me, and turn it into a Win situation.<br>&nbsp;<br>Aeldwan the Enchanter<br>Wanderers of the Realm<br>Morell-Thule<br>"Doing the improbable daily to make the impossible look easy"</td></tr>
