	   <tr><td colspan=2>If you're a good race, go to the outpost in Firiona Vie.&nbsp;&nbsp;That's the little town that you dock to when you take the boat to Kunark from Butcherblock in case you didn't know that.  It's sold in the outpost.  i.e. If you cross the stone bridge to the grassy areas you've gone too far.<br><br>If you're an evil race, go to the Dark Elf outpost in the Overthere.  This is where you end up when you jump on the raft from Oasis of Marr and switch to the bigger 'boat' in Timorous Deep.  Again, if you wander past the outpost in to the grassy area, you've gone too far.<br><br>Have fun.<br><br>-Yizz<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
