	   <tr><td colspan=2>I was just wondering if there were any tips out there that would help me along. I am only a 12 chanter, I just wanted to know where the best place to hunt for my lvl is, or spells that I need, and spells I shouldent bother with, also tips of jewel craft, or anything that might help.<br>Seldara, Terris-Thule<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
